reviews.review_text: Four Words Scarlet Fire Sailor Saint

Holes in what's left of my reason The stream was missing the first 3 songs....very well played show, more frantic sounding than the Starlight show...sounds like they're playing for a hyped up crowd....love the jam out of Saint, nice jam after drums. Good sound too.

It's an obsession but it's pleasin' if for no other reason grab this one up for Lazy Lightning>Supplication. 

2nd set is some real sweet jamming... very underrated show, easily one of my favs from '82, if not right at the top. 

5-star sound, at least 4 to 4.5 on the performance.
